      "content": "makes sense. i was thinking the same thing. but some of my colleagues were arguing that \"culture\" should be more central to the definition of refinement. they think Option B actually has more \"culture\" than Option A. why do you think Option A is more \"refined\" than something like the Meridian District, which is so deeply rooted in arts and heritage?",
